<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Exercise 11 - Cards & Media Layouts</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container my-5" style="max-width: 500px;">
        <h2>11. Cards & Element Components</h2>
        <h4 class="mt-4 text-muted">Exercise 11.1: Component Profile Structure</h4>
        <div class="card mb-5 shadow-sm">
            <div class="bg-secondary text-white text-center py-5 rounded-top" style="font-size: 24px;">
                User Profile Placeholder Graphic
            </div>
            <div class="card-body">
                <h5 class="card-title">Alexander Vance</h5>
                <p class="card-text">Principal Software Operations Architect specialized in clean UI development patterns and utility framework distributions.</p>
                <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary btn-sm">Access System Core Profile</a>
            </div>
        </div>
        <h4 class="text-muted">Exercise 11.2: Flex Layout Media Element</h4>
        <div class="d-flex align-items-start border p-3 rounded bg-light">
            <div class="bg-primary text-white rounded text-center p-3 me-3" style="width: 64px; height: 64px;">
                IMG
            </div>
            <div>
                <h5 class="mt-0">Nested Response Context Title</h5>
                <p class="mb-0 text-secondary" style="font-size: 14px;">This layout aligns a graphic item cleanly on the left of incoming long text comments inside an application loop.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>